{"tid":516597,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"CES 2018 - 集中討論","createTime":"2018-01-01T14:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T12:16:56.000Z","uid":5020,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"19ca7f90aa15154168b85cf4b4ef4740d81cc956","tid":516597,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"一年一度不可錯過全世界最大消費性電子大展CES將於2018年1月9日至1月12日於拉斯維加斯舉辦第51屆CES展覽會。<br />\n<br />\n在2017第50屆CES展覽會上，共有來自150個國家的4400多家廠商參與，約20000多個新產品在展會上推出，參觀者超過15.3萬人次，其中海外參觀者達3.4萬人次，5000家以上媒體報導此次盛會，共舉辦41場主題演講，200場學術研討會。<br />\n<br />\n2018年將展出消費電子產品、視聽器材、影音設備、電腦多媒體及相關週邊設備產品、有線無線通訊設備及配件、家庭安全系統、汽車電子產品及配件、個人消費電子產品及電子零組件等。<br />\n<br />\n今年大會分類:<br />\n<strong>ADVERTISING, ENTERTAINMENT &amp; CONTENT</strong><br />\nGaming<br />\nMarketing &amp; Advertising<br />\nMusic<br />\nVirtual Reality<br />\n<br />\n<strong>AUTOMOTIVE</strong><br />\nSelf-Driving Cars<br />\nVehicle Technology<br />\n<br />\n<strong>HEALTH &amp; WELLNESS</strong><br />\nAccessibility<br />\nDigital Health<br />\nFitness &amp; Wearables<br />\nSleep Technology<br />\n<br />\n<strong>HOME &amp; FAMILY</strong><br />\nFamily &amp; Lifestyle<br />\nHome Entertainment<br />\nSmart Home<br />\n<br />\n<strong>INTERNET OF THINGS (IoT)</strong><br />\nSmart Cities<br />\nSmart Energy<br />\n<br />\n<strong>PRODUCT DESIGN &amp; MANUFACTURING</strong><br />\n3D Printing<br />\nDesign, Sourcing &amp; Packaging<br />\n<br />\n<strong>ROBOTICS &amp; MACHINE INTELLIGENCE</strong><br />\nArtificial Intelligence<br />\nDrones<br />\nRobotics<br />\n<br />\n<strong>SPORTS</strong><br />\neSports &amp; eLeagues<br />\nSport Technology<br />\n<br />\n<strong>STARTUPS</strong><br />\nInvestors<br />\nStartups<br />\n<br />\nCES 官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ces.tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ces.tech%2F&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=303ef063\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ces.tech/</a><br />\n<br />\nNvidia CES 2018 專頁:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nvidia.com.tw/object/ces-2018-tw.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nvidia.com.tw%2Fobject%2Fces-2018-tw.html&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=112ee278\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nvidia.com.tw/object/ces-2018-tw.html</a><br />\n<br />\nSony CES 2018 專頁:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/sony-ces-latest-products\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com.hk%2Fzh%2Felectronics%2Fsony-ces-latest-products&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=c79dd029\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/sony-ces-latest-products</a>"},{"pid":"6043a5dc3007b4997fefab10a9dd6579757fe47d","tid":516597,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"CES 11月時嘅預展片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gDe_WKVShJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgDe_WKVShJg&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=10cbdddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gDe_WKVShJg</a>"},{"pid":"ab06b27e92ccdcd8141f13e10137c053f83dba98","tid":516597,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"CES 時間表<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ces.tech/Logistics/Dates-and-Hours\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ces.tech%2FLogistics%2FDates-and-Hours&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=4bdec7cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ces.tech/Logistics/Dates-and-Hours</a>"},{"pid":"0ee05c485cf9fd4adbc9e6fe1486eb45de0ae09f","tid":516597,"uid":64401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"HDMI 2.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5637847885dac94424fd8ac0c4c20f07a094f7","tid":516597,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ee05c485cf9fd4adbc9e6fe1486eb45de0ae09f","tid":516597